title: BlackCat
description:
PLEASE SEED

Carries repetitive riffs like Editors with the chord structure of Elefant and the vocals of Kim Carnes. A dash of Yellowcard and a hint of Feeder and you might just create BlackCat.

We encourage you to share these tracks, and allow you to use them for projects such as youtube videos, podcasts, radio stations etc providing that give credit to the artist
